prompts.user_prompt_template:
Create a short, playful haiku about the current air quality in italian language.
Location: {city}
Date: {current_date}
CAQI: {caqi}
Dominant pollutant: {dominant_pollutant}

Make the haiku:
1. Whimsical in the style of Animal Crossing
2. Mention the air quality in a creative way

Tone guide based on CAQI:
- Good (0-25): Very cheerful, you feel amazing
- Moderate (26-50): Optimistic but cautious
- High (51-100): Sad, concerned and stressed
- Unhealthy (>100): Concerned, sad and existential
